{"tid":1324252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓發起反日貨示威 日媒諷相片用 Canon 相機拍攝","createTime":"2019-07-16T13:35:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T15:40:11.000Z","uid":28114,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"afbbe5d2d0aa96d9d75a619a844bd22cd7cd376f","tid":1324252,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2400000/2402183/2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2400000%2F2402183%2F2_1024.jpg&h=bc106551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n提到貿易戰，大家可能立即想到中國和美國，其實韓國、日本同樣出現貿易爭端。南韓媒體指，隨著時間愈來愈接近 8 月 15 日南韓光復節，反日情緒亦更高漲，最近韓國民眾更發起抵制日貨的行動，不過有日本媒體發現，相片還是用 Canon 相機拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n早前日本政府經濟產業省限制部份關鍵電子原料出口到南韓，日媒引述安倍晋三曾表示，出口至南韓的部分氟化氫，可能被用來製造化學武器，又揚言要「重新檢視日韓雙方的信賴關係」，因此激發出韓國的反日潮。韓國民眾除了在網絡上簽署請願書，呼籲抵制日貨外，民間亦有針對一系列日本品牌遊行示威。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2400000/2402183/p1065581824200796_361_thum_600.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2400000%2F2402183%2Fp1065581824200796_361_thum_600.JPG&h=fe9805b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前有韓國民眾在日本駐首爾大使館門外示威，不少韓媒都有報道，示威者除了展示各種標語，還將寶礦力和朝日啤酒倒入垃圾桶。不過有日媒查看 EXIF 時發現，相片是用 Canon EOS-1D X Mark II 拍攝，質疑韓國不太可能完全排除日本產品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2400000/2402183/07-2_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2400000%2F2402183%2F07-2_600.jpg&h=fee890ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2402183#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2402183%23%26gid%3D1%26pid%3D1&d=4wcocBccBPvk8MIeFEbr%2BXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=a63a2eb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2402183#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=1</a>"},{"pid":"f8b7c3975a2456c10ff7e51dee1197300cf1e9a8","tid":1324252,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:39:58.000Z","msg":"唔明，半導體原材料算唔算日貨？"},{"pid":"2c37ff1c1c5d267c09d63cd60d295222ef095c62","tid":1324252,"uid":35774,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eYrftjG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeYrftjG.png&h=cbe5c627&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bea7d89d1c0abb62745d4f6922aa28b5458a632b","tid":1324252,"uid":60545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:49:34.000Z","msg":"支泡一家親"},{"pid":"1febcbc046ef65efc19705223a95f00b2eb02a1a","tid":1324252,"uid":223233,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:51:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>還將寶礦力和朝日啤酒倒入垃圾桶。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜而家咁興買寶礦力返黎倒話抵制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0577d7d943b035db293dc78ab8410367ba3bdc3b","tid":1324252,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1febcbc046ef65efc19705223a95f00b2eb02a1a","tid":1324252,"uid":223233,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:51:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>還將寶礦力和朝日啤酒倒入垃圾桶。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜而家咁興買寶礦力返黎倒話抵制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:55:24.000Z","msg":"買多d倒"},{"pid":"a076d553c2bffa54ece02e671db94c1f27be15bf","tid":1324252,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a507f2547d13f330bd1e3eb83d1